# Cursor AI Rules for SSBC Project

## Environment Setup
When running terminal commands or Python scripts in this project, always use the `ssbc` mamba environment:

- **For one-off commands**: `mamba run -n ssbc <command>`
- **For Python scripts**: `mamba run -n ssbc python <script>`
- **For interactive shells**: Start with `mamba activate ssbc` or `source .envrc-conda`
- **For pytest**: `mamba run -n ssbc pytest <args>`
- **For any Python tool**: `mamba run -n ssbc <tool> <args>`

## Examples
```bash
# Run tests
mamba run -n ssbc pytest

# Run Python script
mamba run -n ssbc python examples/basic_usage.py

# Install package
mamba run -n ssbc pip install <package>

# Activate for multiple commands
mamba activate ssbc
```
